flowchart TD
    A[data/songs.csv] -->|load_songs| B[List of Song dicts]
    U[User Prefs<br/>genres, moods, target_energy,<br/>target_valence, target_tempo, etc.] --> R

    B --> R{recommend_songs loop}
    R -->|for each song| F{Already heard?<br/>id in already_heard_ids}
    F -->|Yes| X[Skip song]
    F -->|No| S[score_song]

    S --> S1[closeness on energy, valence,<br/>danceability, acousticness, tempo]
    S --> S2[genre match? 1.0 or 0.0]
    S --> S3[mood match? 1.0 or 0.0]
    S1 --> W[Weighted sum<br/>using WEIGHTS dict]
    S2 --> W
    S3 --> W
    W --> SC[score + reasons list]

    SC --> AC[Append song, score, explanation<br/>to scored list]
    AC --> R
    R -->|loop done| SORT[Sort scored by score DESC]
    SORT --> TOP[Take top k = 5]
    TOP --> OUT[Print title, score, reasons]
